</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/essay/do-not-repeat-liza-martin" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/MartinCot-w.jpg?itok=Rryz3rEY" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of a cot in a dimly lit prison cell" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

